description: Keychain storage and App Transport Security rules
alwaysApply: false
globs: ["**/*.swift"]
---

# Security

- Keychain for API keys, base URLs; kSecAttrAccessibleWhenUnlockedThisDeviceOnly
- No iCloud sync for server credentials
- ATS: NSAllowsLocalNetworking for self-hosted; per-domain exceptions
- Never embed secrets in source; never log credentials
